Emphasizes the need to ensure respect for the human rights and fundamental freedoms of women and children in Afghanistan and to end and prevent all abuses against women and children, encourages the full implementation of the Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Discrimination against Women
United Nations, Treaty Series, vol. 1249, No. 20378. and the Convention on the Rights of the Child and the Optional Protocols thereto,
Ibid., vol. 1577, vol. 2171, vol. 2173, vol. 2983, No. 27531. and strongly condemns all forms of violence against women and children;
